code:
name: chunk
services:
  devcontainer:
    container_name: devcontainer
    build:
      context: .
      dockerfile: .devcontainer/Dockerfile
    volumes:
      - ./:/workspace:rw
    environment:
      - AUTH0_DOMAIN=${AUTH0_DOMAIN}
      - AUTH0_CLIENT_ID=${AUTH0_CLIENT_ID}
    command: sleep infinity
